OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe Princess Royal has visited Co
OL,7,FFermanagh to celebrate the 85th
OL,8,Fanniversary of the Air Training Corps.
OL,10,FAnne met air cadets from across
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland on her engagement in
OL,12,Fthe region on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe princess paid her respects at the
OL,15,FCommonwealth war graves at St
OL,16,FTighernach's Church of Ireland and
OL,17,FSacred Heart Church, Irvinestown,
OL,18,Fwhere 86 airmen who died in the Second
OL,19,FWorld War are laid to rest.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
