FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,FShe also planted an Irish yew tree
OL,7,Fduring a visit to the Castle Archdale
OL,8,FMuseum and heard music played by the
OL,9,FBallyreagh Silver Band.
OL,11,FAccompanied by RAF representatives and
OL,12,Fcadets, Anne met young people from the
OL,13,FRAF Air Cadets and was told about the
OL,14,Flives and service of those
OL,15,Fcommemorated at the sites.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
