PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAt Castle Archdale, the former Royal
OL,7,FAir Force flying boat station on Lower
OL,8,FLough Erne, she met relatives of
OL,9,Fformer Women's Auxiliary Air Force
OL,10,Fpersonnel who served there and heard
OL,11,Fabout the station's wartime
OL,12,Fcontribution to maritime patrol and
OL,13,Fanti-submarine operations.
OL,15,FShe also viewed exhibits showcasing
OL,16,Fthe RAF's current capabilities and
OL,17,Fobserved a flypast by a Royal Air
OL,18,FForce Poseidon aircraft from No. 201
OL,19,FSquadron.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
