FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,FWing Commander Chris Hodges, the OC of
OL,7,Fthe RAF Cadets in Northern Ireland,
OL,8,Fsaid it was a "great privilege" to
OL,9,Fhave Anne there on the anniversary.
OL,11,F"We are particularly pleased with the
OL,12,Fprogress our new unit in Enniskillen
OL,13,Fhas made in the last 18 months," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Thank you to the good people of Co
OL,17,FFermanagh for their ongoing support"
