PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAir Officer Northern Ireland, Air
OL,7,FMarshal Sean Reynolds, said: "I am
OL,8,Fdelighted that the Air Cadet
OL,9,FOrganisation in Northern Ireland are
OL,10,Fcelebrating the 85th anniversary of
OL,11,Fthe Air Training Corps in Fermanagh.
OL,13,F"RAF Air Cadets have played an
OL,14,Fimportant role over their history both
OL,15,Fin terms of their contribution to the
OL,16,FRAF, but also promoting the RAF's
OL,17,Fvalues and developing young people to
OL,18,Fbecome good citizens.
OL,26,@oD@^OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
