OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784830711
OL,3,CPrincess Anne met air cadets from
OL,4,Cacross Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"It is also fitting recognition of our
OL,7,Fadult volunteers without whom the Air
OL,8,FCadet Organisation would not exist.
OL,10,F"It is appropriate that we are able to
OL,11,Fcelebrate this today, in both
OL,12,FIrvinestown and Castle Archdale,
OL,13,Frecognising its history, achievements
OL,14,Fand continued contribution to young
OL,15,Fpeople, the Royal Air Force and
OL,16,Fcommunities in Northern Ireland."
